dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Chippewa County, WI 2016
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Chippewa County, Wisconsin in 2016. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Chippewa_Hydro_2016.gdb. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Chippewa_Water_Lines' and 'Chippewa_Water_Polygons'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
